NAME
----

Lingua-EO-Orthography (Perl module Lingua::EO::Orthography)

INSTALLATION
------------

To install this distribution,

first, to make Makefile, build this distribution and run tests
by the following command:

    % cpan -t .

next, to deploy this distribution
by the following command:

    % cpan -i .

DEPENDENCIES
------------

See "Makefile.PL".

DOCUMENTATION
-------------

Lingua::EO::Orthography documentation is available as in POD.
So you can do:

    % perldoc Lingua::EO::Orthography

to read the documentation online with your favorite pager.

